{"tid":494420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[置業找叮噹] 水管屋助港青上樓夢 可容1至2人住","createTime":"2017-12-09T15:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T16:17:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac00f4c82d077f54f07657313dcbe50d69eb503","tid":494420,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"香港房屋問題嚴重，建築師羅發禮設計「水管屋」，希望以平價及環保方法協助年輕人解決房屋問題。水管屋更首次在香港貿易發展局主辦的國際創意設計博覽上展出。<br />\n<br />\n羅指，眼見現時香港年輕人難以「上樓」，因此設計以混凝土水管構成的居所。羅設計的水管屋約100呎，可供1至2人居住，亦配備煮食和浴室設施。水管屋可疊高成3至4層，組成低層建築。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171209/photo/bkn-20171209113817691-1209_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171209142532\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171209%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171209113817691-1209_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171209142532&h=40ea0377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171209/bkn-20171209113817691-1209_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171209%2Fbkn-20171209113817691-1209_00822_001.html&d=rJjrve1ULVWJd0Foy4hClG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=405a8c98\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171209/bkn-20171209113817691-1209_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"25902b3841855273f8b076cdf37e4aa66cc89f9e","tid":494420,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/231117_8b95209b87f05be2d84695c5112ab165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F231117_8b95209b87f05be2d84695c5112ab165.jpg&h=fc1a364f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db963f27b6640bcec9e3d8387634b51c0e625d16","tid":494420,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:13:08.000Z","msg":"幾得意呀，如果平既，唔介意租黎住，單身想自由既，呢d幾正"},{"pid":"c4c4d61ec5a3db5de54171af92735bb0e3cfa9c2